      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1>Thinking deeply about children in society.</h1>&nbsp;<h2>Style Mode: Presets</h2><p>Native includes two preset styles, Light &amp; Dark. These are meant to be good starting points for you to begin customizing the colors and fonts the way you want.</p>
  
      <img src="http://static1.squarespace.com/static/501c8d6b24ac0a1285ed8244/t/501c8d6c24ac0a1285ed8282/1342797084097/style-presets.png?format=original" alt=""/>
  

