</div>&nbsp;<h2>Style Mode: Sizes &amp; Values</h2><p>Native lets you control the widths of major website sections like the Site, Blog Content and Page Content areas. You also get control over certain sections of padding.</p>
  
      <img src="http://static1.squarespace.com/static/501c8d6b24ac0a1285ed8244/t/501c8d6c24ac0a1285ed8274/1342814008198/style-sizes.png?format=original" alt=""/>
  


  
