&nbsp;<h2>Blog Post With Promoted Block</h2><p>If the <strong>very first block</strong> in your post is not floated or added to a column &amp; contains <strong>one</strong> of the following: <strong>Image, Gallery, Video or Quote</strong>... it will 'promote' the element above the title and allow it to use the full site width.</p>
  
      <img src="http://static1.squarespace.com/static/501c8d6b24ac0a1285ed8244/t/501c8d6b24ac0a1285ed826d/1343056599330/promoted-type-icons.png?format=original" alt=""/>
  

<div class="image-gallery-wrapper">

  
