&nbsp;<h2>Mobile Responsive Layouts Are Built Right In—For Tablet &amp; Smartphone Resolutions&nbsp;</h2><p>On smaller screen sizes, the template responds to the lower resolution and / or smaller canvas with adjusted sizes, heights and layouts so it just fits.</p>
  
